description: Human evolution was built around the constant striving of stability. We crave to built a foundation which will make us resilient to what the future will present us. But stability is illusion if perceived as a static notion. The only way to keep balance is constant movement with the right speed and focus. The momentum will help you to overcome an uneven surface, and synergy of strength and focus will provide you with the ability to make elegant manoeuvres.
